Jay Jay, my dawg, my son you are missed and I know you’re having a great time in heaven with Chewie. Thanks for being there for me and with me through everything. Thanks for growing up with me. You were there when i made my first song, You were there before I even knew I had a dream we’ve watched countless hours of anime together and grateful to have been blessed with a dog as kind and charismatic as you were. Thanks for keeping me company and checking on me whenever I was down or up.  Thank you for being ready to protect us when things looked sketchy. I promised to ice out your collar maybe one day I’ll get one for your daughter. Thanks for blessing the world with 8 great puppies. I love you Jay Jay see you when I see you again. ✌️❤️🐶
